%% Circuit breaker state machine - one breaker, many trigger codes
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Armed: engine start

    Armed --> Minor: minor breach<br/>stale_tick, wide_spread, stale_market_data
    Minor --> Armed: cooldown elapsed

    Armed --> Major: major breach<br/>drawdown, reconcile, operator_halt
    Major --> Latched: flatten triggered
    Latched --> Armed: operator rearm

    state Armed {
        [*] --> EntriesAllowed
        EntriesAllowed --> EntriesAllowed: pre-trade checks pass
    }

    state Minor {
        [*] --> EntryVeto
        EntryVeto --> WaitingCooldown
        WaitingCooldown --> [*]: breaker.tick()
    }

    state Major {
        [*] --> PauseAndFlatten
        PauseAndFlatten --> BlockEntries
        BlockEntries --> [*]
    }

    note right of Armed
        PreTradeValidator checks
        breaker state before entries.
    end note

    note right of Major
        Reduce-only exits remain allowed
        so flattening can still reach the venue.
    end note
